## üçä Orange 

### Should I sum, count or average? 

When to use each:

| Function | Purpose | Example Use Cases |
|----------|---------|-----------------|
| SUM | Adds all values together within a group | ‚Ä¢ Total hours spent on sleep across all regions<br>‚Ä¢ Combined fare paid by all first-class Titanic passengers<br>‚Ä¢ Total duration of all songs in the Pop genre |
| COUNT | Tallies the number of instances/rows in each group | ‚Ä¢ Number of passengers in each Titanic class<br>‚Ä¢ Count of countries per region in the Global Human Day dataset<br>‚Ä¢ How many songs fall into each playlist genre |
| MEAN | Calculates the average value within a group | ‚Ä¢ Average danceability of songs by artist<br>‚Ä¢ Average ticket price by class <br>‚Ä¢ Mean hours spent on childcare activities by region |

